 Gog his son, Shimei his son,","year":-1710},{"id":"recqtiQHvDRIyL5si","ref":"1Chr.5.5","text":"Micah his son, Reaia his son, Baal his son,","year":-1710},{"id":"recTLfeIwXXiRswXs","ref":"1Chr.5.6","text":"Beerah his son, whom Tilgathpilneser king of Assyria carried away captive: he was prince of the Reubenites.","year":-1710},{"id":"rec268Bwv65jFW774","ref":"1Chr.5.7","text":"And his brethren by their families, when the genealogy of their generations was reckoned, were the chief, Jeiel, and Zechariah,","year":-1710},{"id":"recGzPEuXfGcFiFlE","ref":"1Chr.5.8","text":"And Bela the son of Azaz, the son of Shema, the son of Joel, who dwelt in Aroer, even unto Nebo and Baalmeon:","year":-1710}]}
